The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of neural networks, which could place it under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
